---
// TrainingTeachers - Seção explicativa sobre professores em treinamento
// Usado nas LPs: recovery, promo
---

<section class="training-section" id="professores">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-badge">Entenda o Sistema</span>
      <h2>O que são os Professores em Treinamento?</h2>
      <p>Conheça o rigoroso processo de formação dos professores QQEnglish</p>
    </div>

    <div class="training-grid">
      <!-- Imagem do processo -->
      <div class="training-visual reveal">
        <img 
          src="/images/teacher-training.webp" 
          alt="Processo de treinamento dos professores QQEnglish" 
          width="600" 
          height="400"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Explicação -->
      <div class="training-content reveal">
        <div class="training-intro">
          <p>
            Todos os professores QQEnglish passam por um <strong>programa intensivo de 550+ horas</strong> 
            de treinamento antes de se tornarem professores gerais. Durante esse período, eles são 
            classificados como <strong>professores em treinamento</strong> (5 a 40 pontos).
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="training-steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>40 horas - Onboard Training</h4>
              <p>Treinamento básico de ensino ESL e metodologia online</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>105 horas - Certificação TESOL</h4>
              <p>Obtenção da certificação internacional de ensino de inglês</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>550 horas - Advanced OJT</h4>
              <p>Treinamento prático supervisionado com alunos reais</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="training-highlight">
          <div class="highlight-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/>
              <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight-text">
            <strong>Seus 24 tickets</strong> dão acesso a esses professores em treinamento — 
            em treinamento para certificação TESOL, supervisionados por professores veteranos, perfeitos para maximizar sua prática de conversação!
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Comparativo -->
    <div class="teacher-comparison reveal">
      <h3>Comparativo de Professores</h3>
      <div class="comparison-cards">
        <div class="comparison-card training">
          <div class="card-header">
            <span class="card-badge">5-40 pts</span>
            <h4>Em Treinamento</h4>
          </div>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Em formação TESOL
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Supervisionados por veteranos
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Ótimo para prática intensiva
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Melhor custo-benefício
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="card-footer">
            <span class="use-case">Ideal para: Volume de prática</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="comparison-card general">
          <div class="card-header">
            <span class="card-badge">50+ pts</span>
            <h4>Professores Gerais</h4>
          </div>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              550+ horas de experiência
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Experiência com diversos perfis
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Feedback mais detalhado
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
              </svg>
              Especialização em métodos
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="card-footer">
            <span class="use-case">Ideal para: Objetivos específicos</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .training-section {
    padding: var(--section-padding, 5rem 0);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fafc 0%, #fff 100%);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.375rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2563eb;
    background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    color: #1a1a2e;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #6b7280;
  }

  .training-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .training-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .training-visual img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .training-intro {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #374151;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .training-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #1d4ed8);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step-content h4 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #1a1a2e;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .step-content p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #6b7280;
  }

  .training-highlight {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1), rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.05));
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
  }

  .highlight-icon {
    color: #2563eb;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .highlight-text {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #374151;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Comparison Cards */
  .teacher-comparison {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .teacher-comparison h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #1a1a2e;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .comparison-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .comparison-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .comparison-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    text-align: left;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .comparison-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  .comparison-card.training {
    border-color: #10b981;
  }

  .comparison-card.general {
    border-color: #2563eb;
  }

  .card-header {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .card-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .training .card-badge {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
    color: #059669;
  }

  .general .card-badge {
    background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
    color: #2563eb;
  }

  .card-header h4 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #1a1a2e;
  }

  .comparison-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .comparison-card li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #374151;
  }

  .comparison-card li svg {
    color: #10b981;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .card-footer {
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
  }

  .use-case {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* Reveal animation */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: all 0.6s ease;
  }

  .reveal.is-visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
</style>
